data.description: Welcome to this contemporary ranch, awaiting your personal touch to transform it into your dream home. Embrace the potential for modernization with a new kitchen and flooring, promising to elevate its appeal to new heights. Cherished by a single family since its inception, this home radiates warmth and care. Recent updates include a Trane HVAC system, water heater, driveway, sidewalks and roof. Step inside to discover vaulted ceilings gracing the living, dining rooms, and den (can be converted to a 3rd main level bedroom)l, providing spacious ambiance. Huge kitchen presents ample room for cabinetry, a generous island, and a breakfast area, promising both functionality and style. Lower level features a convenient walk-out and abundant natural light filtering through numerous windows.Outside, the level backyard is perfect for summertime gatherings and outdoor activities. Ideally situated in Parkway School district minutes from Creve Coeur Park/Lake, shopping destinations, and highways.
